data.description: Don't miss out on this one! 6 bed 5 bath on 1 acre in Good Hope School district. Huge living room with beautiful fireplace. Wood floor under the carpet in the living room. Large kitchen with pantry, dining room and breakfast nook. The basement is fully finished with a full kitchen, dining room, living room, bathroom, bedroom and large walk in closet. 2 car garage as well as a carport. Large storage building conveys. Pool is 1 year old. New HVAC was installed in 2018.
